{
	// REGULAR DIALOGUE
	"jenny_dialogue.Introduction": "So you're the new kid everyone has been flipping out over.#$b#Welcome to town, my hours are 9 to 6, now go away, I've got shit to do.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Mon": "Can't you see I'm busy, kid?",
	"jenny_dialogue.Tue": "What do you want? I've got a business to run.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Wed": "Do you need something?",
	"jenny_dialogue.Thu": "Listen, kid, I can't help you. Unless you want to order a sandwich or something, get lost.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Fri": "Sunday can't come soon enough. I need a fucking break.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Sat": "Some fucking raccoon or something keeps digging through my trash.#$3#That's what I get for settling down in the fucking countryside...",
	"jenny_dialogue.Sun": "Living in a tiny town sucks in a lot of ways, but at least the rent here is way lower.",
	
	"jenny_dialogue.Mon2": "Don't you have actual work to do instead of bothering me?",
	"jenny_dialogue.Tue2": "Jesus, kid, don't sneak up on me like that. I have a cleaver and you could lose an arm.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Wed2": "Got any produce for me? Pork is pretty popular in {{Season}}. I'll pay a little extra.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Thu2": "Chicken's half off today. I'll throw in a free sandwich if you buy in bulk.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Fri2": "Has anyone ever told you you're really persistent?",
	"jenny_dialogue.Sat2": "At least I have tomorrow off... don't know what I'll do. Probably watch TV in my pajamas. Or catch up on inventory...",
	"jenny_dialogue.Sun2": "I didn't think I needed to say this, but no running in the shop. Do I need to put up a sign?",
	
	"jenny_dialogue.Mon4": "I swear, next time the girls try to pay their rent in cursed pirate gold, or a jar of nickels, or anything that isn't cold, hard cash, I'm kicking them out.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Tue4": "I couldn't sleep last night for all the banging and thumping coming from upstairs. If I didn't know it was stupid \"Agency business\" I would've thought we were being robbed.#$b#I told them to keep it down, but they'll probably be back at it again soon.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Wed4": "",
	"jenny_dialogue.Thu4": "Can I convince you to buy some trout? It's going bad soon, and I don't want to have to throw it out.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Fri4": "Got any produce to sell? I'll take what Pierre doesn't want.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Sat4": "Gus ordered some prime cuts of beef last week. He must be cooking up something new.#$b#He's half my business, to be honest.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Sun4": "Now I know how Pierre's been in business so long. His prices are ridiculous.",
	
	"jenny_dialogue.Mon6": "Next time you see Crystal, tell her to tone down the amount of 4am ghost conversations? She clearly doesn't listen to me about it.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Tue6": "Ugh. I have a headache almost as bad as that time a demon possessed me.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Wed6": "Sigh... How did Dad do it? He made running the shop look so easy.#$b#Actually, it was probably all the cigs and liquor. Never mind.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Thu6": "The shop only closes one day a week, but there's still never enough time to do everything.#$b#Maybe I'll waive a week of rent if one of the girls helps out.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Fri6": "Everyone else's week is almost over, but not mine.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Sat6": "",
	"jenny_dialogue.Sun6": "I don't know how I'm going to pay taxes this week... Why did I think a butcher shop could work in a town full of pescatarians?",
	
	"jenny_dialogue.Mon8": "Ugh, I got such a slow start this morning.#$b#The boys forgot that humans sleep at normal hours and tried to start a conversation about wards on the shop at 5am.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Tue8": "Pelican Town is even smaller than where I grew up, and that's saying something. Way fewer evil witches and shit though.#$e#Well, until Esther came back.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Wed8": "You know, I appreciate how normal you are compared to everyone else in my life.#$e#Even if the scale is permanently broken.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Thu8": "I kind of lost my taste for true crime documentaries recently. Now I have to fall asleep to Queen of Sauce... half the time I dream about sinking under a giant pile of food.#$b#Probably symbolic of my shitty work-life balance or something.#$e#At least it's better than nightmares...",
	"jenny_dialogue.Fri8": "I don't think Marnie likes me very much. I get that animals are her whole thing, but it's the circle of life. Even me and you will be a pile of meat and bones someday.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Sat8": "Mrs. Mullner dropped off some cookies earlier. I may know how to butcher, but the way she bakes is something else. #$b#No, get your own.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Sun8": "Niko keeps inviting me to the library.#$b#I don't know how to tell her it brings back awful memories.#$e#What happened? Oh, just a bad date. Local librarian turned murderous stalker who couldn't take no for an answer.#$e#She died, so...",
	
	"jenny_dialogue.Mon10": "What recipe should I prepare for next week's demonstration, do you think? The last one was pretty popular.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Tue10": "It's not that I don't want to find a partner... I just don't know how I can ever trust someone again. You know the feeling?",
	"jenny_dialogue.Wed10": "I'm trying to quit smoking. But I've been trying to quit for four years, so...",
	"jenny_dialogue.Thu10": "I can't leave Monty alone in the shop yet, but I can at least get other work done while he's at the register.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Fri10": "...#$b#I'm really glad we have Niko back. When she died, it was...#$b#Anyway.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Sat10": "I worry about Charles sometimes.#$b#I mean, I worry about all of them, as many gray hairs as it gives me.#$b#But he's a lot like me at that age, except teenage Jenny was worse at hiding her feelings.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Sun10": "Don't tell Edwin I told you, but we've been listening to mystery podcasts together when the shop isn't busy.#$e#Don't tell him I told you this, either, but it's actually not a bad time.",
	
	"jenny_dialogue.Wed_6": "Whatever you're doing on that farm, it's working.#$b#I haven't seen such good produce in years.",
	"jenny_dialogue.Sun_6": "Ugh. My supplier is fucking late, *again*.$a",
	"jenny_dialogue.summer_1": "Ugh, it's too fucking hot out for this.",
	"jenny_dialogue.winter_1": "Ugh, it's too fucking cold out for this.",
	
	// STRINGS
	
	// GIFT TASTE
	"JennyButcher.love": "Who told you I like this?$a#$b#Never mind... thanks.",
	"JennyButcher.like": "You have good taste, kid.",
	"JennyButcher.dislike": "Whatever.",
	"JennyButcher.hate": "What the fuck, @?",
	"JennyButcher.neutral": "Thanks.",
}